class Conn extends EventTarget
  A connection that fires events when its state changes.

  @event open
      Fired when the connection opens.

  @event close
      Fired when the connection closes.


  open(): void
    Open the connection.

    @fires Conn#open
  close(): void
    Close the connection.

    @fires Conn#close
  subscribe(): void
    Subscribe to the upstream feed.

    @listens Conn#open

